{"tid":1506901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大陸都有唔少異議的網民在牆內發聲","createTime":"2019-08-26T03:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T06:31:58.000Z","uid":293557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"98918a882d918ad39e61f125ef22462fe52b026e","tid":1506901,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XfdD1rH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXfdD1rH.jpg&h=012382e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身之前睇左網易好耐, 早幾年comment都百花齊放<br />\n有一段時間, 除左&quot;頂&quot;, 都仲有 &quot;踩&quot;, 但好快就取消, 驚俾網民發泄<br />\n而一的重大, 涉及領導人/朝鮮的帖, 大多都唔俾評論<br />\n<br />\n但有一項統計, 一直都俾明眼人見到民意端倪<br />\n好似上面跟貼98, 萬幾人參與, 一睇就知唔正常<br />\n好明顯近乎99%的評論都係審貼時出唔到, 可能有的係偏激, 有的係暗諷, 但都唔俾出街<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解一路留住呢個統計, 可能小編覺得係另一種無聲的抗議<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家見到內地網上一面倒的文宣唔好灰心, 其實有良心的內地網民一直試緊支持我地！"},{"pid":"517a1e0180d59cfd7584e46363b36d3173096e3d","tid":1506901,"uid":293557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxBx50A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxBx50A.jpg&h=530b3547&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n但最令人氣憤的莫過於將&quot;老翻&quot; 五大訴求當港人心聲, 可能呢個就正正係建制提另一版本5大訴求的動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扭曲民意, 顛倒黑白, 正正係國內網絡最可怕最黑暗之處"},{"pid":"29008b66bfc14e015b189b9c72e2bef4c1eda35f","tid":1506901,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T06:31:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/search/top/?q=%E5%85%B1%E7%94%A2%E9%BB%A8%E6%8E%9B%E7%BE%8A%E9%A0%AD%20%E8%B3%A3%E7%8B%97%E8%82%89%20%E8%AC%9B%E5%98%85%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E5%81%9A%E5%98%85%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%20%E5%91%A2%E7%8F%AD%E7%B4%B0%E8%B7%AF%E5%9A%9F%E5%B9%AB%E4%BD%A0%E5%93%8B%E7%88%AD%E5%8F%96%20%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%20%EF%BC%8C%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%80%